title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 46] New Wave, Post Punk, Synthpop
description:
I am posting these four records, three as requested and to make sure you have enough music to take you through the weekend! A quick note; I had posted A Drop in Gray twice before but both torrents are dead and I see people trying to dl. As I don't have the version I had uploaded before and have ripped a new copy, I am posting it here again. Besides I'd like more people to listen to this gem. Blue Hollow - Stealing a Whisper is my pick and I hope you like it!


A Drop In The Gray - Certain Sculptures [1985]

Blue Hollow - Stealing a whisper [1985]

Crazy House - Still Looking For Heaven On Earth [1987]

Nine Below Zero - Third Degree [1982]
